Cutar cutar coronavirus (COVID-19) da aka yi a Tarayyar Turai/Hukumar Tsaro ta Turai da Majalisar Dinkin Duniya, 1 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020
Cutar coronavirus mai haɗuwa (COVID-19) tana haifar da rikice-rikice kamar yadda Tarayyar Turai/Taron Tsaro na Turai da Tarayyar Burtaniya suka yi, kuma a wani lokaci, ana gudanar da ayyukan COVID-19 a cikin gaggawa a duk faɗin duniya.
Dangane da abin da ya faru a Italiya, asibitoci, asibitoci da kungiyoyin kula da marasa lafiya dole ne su sake tsara shirye-shiryen su saboda yawan masu cutar COVID-19 da ke buƙatar kulawa ta musamman, da kuma ƙarin kulawa ta musamman.
A ranar 31 ga Disamba, 2019, wani taron ta'addanci wanda ba a san sunansa ba ya faru a Wuhan, lardin Hubei, China.
A ranar 9 ga Janairu, 2020, Hukumar Kula da Cututtuka ta kasar Sin ta bayyana cewa sabon kwayar cutar coronavirus da aka sani da cutar sankara ta coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2) ba ta da wata illa.
Tun daga wannan lokacin, cutar da SARS-CoV ke haifarwa ana kiranta cutar (COVI-19).
Binciken da aka yi a baya ya nuna cewa kusan kashi 80% na mutane suna da cutar da ba ta da tsanani, wato cutar da ba ta shafi huhu, kuma ba ta da cutar.
A cikin kashi 14 cikin dari na cutar, COVID-19 ta haifar da rashin lafiya mai tsanani da kuma rayuwa a asibiti kuma kashi 6 cikin dari na marasa lafiya suna da matukar damuwa kuma suna buƙatar kulawa ta likita.
Mutuwar asibiti saboda COVID-19 ya kai kashi 4%.
A cikin wannan binciken, mun bincika yadda ake gudanar da aikin rigakafin COVID-19 a kowace ƙasa ta Tarayyar Turai/EEA da Tarayyar Burtaniya (UK) da kuma wanda ke Hubei, China.
Na kuma bincika adadin masu cutar COVID-19 a yanzu a cikin EU/EEA da UK da waɗanda ke Italiya daga 31 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020.
Cutar COVID-19 a EU/EEA da UK
Bayan China, COVID-19 ya mamaye wasu yankuna kuma yaduwar cutar ta COVID-19 a sauran ƙasashe a duniya yanzu tana bin wannan matakin.
A ranar 11 ga Maris, 2020, Babban Jami'in Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) ya ayyana COVID-19 a matsayin annoba ta duniya.
A cikin rahoton Eurosurveillance na 5 ga Maris, 2020, Spiteri al. ya ba da rahoton farkon bayyanar da cutar COVID-19 a Turai bisa ga WHO.
A cikin EU/EEA, an fara sanar da cutar ta uku ta Faransa a ranar 24 ga Janairu 2020 a cikin mazauna birnin Wuhan, lardin Hubei, China.
A ranar 15 ga Maris, 2020, an gano sabbin cututtukan COVID-19 a cikin ƙasashe 30 na EU/EEA da Tarayyar Burtaniya, wanda a tsakanin 31 ga Disamba, 2019 da kuma wannan lokacin ya nuna cewa akwai masu kamuwa da cutar 39,768 da mutuwar 1,727, da kuma mutuwar 1,441 a cikin Italiya.
Gudanar da lissafin da kuma tattara adadin masu cutar COVID-19
A cewar Hukumar Kula da Cututtuka ta Turai (ECDC), adadin mutanen da suka kamu da cutar COVID-19 a kowace kasa a duniya, wanda aka ba da shawarar ga hukumomin da suka fi dacewa kamar su Ma'aikatar Lafiya ta Duniya, hukumomin cikin gida da na gari da WHO za a sake tantance su a ranar 8 na yamma.
An yi amfani da bayanan don yin gwajin COVID-19 a cikin EU/EEA da Burtaniya, tare da kwatanta rayuwa da na Italiya.
A matsayin kimantawa na yawan masu kamuwa da cutar ta COVID-19, mun lissafa haɗuwa da masu kamuwa da cutar ta COVID-19, ta hanyar kimanta yanayin COVID-19 a kowace ƙasar EU/EEA da Burtaniya daga 1 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris 2020.
Mun kuma gano jimillar adadin wadanda suka kamu da cutar a kowace kasa a ranar 15 ga Maris 2020 da karfe 8:00 na yamma, wanda ya shafi Italiya daga ranar 31 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris 2020.
Yanayin COVID-19 a cikin EU/EEA da UK.
Ci gaban da aka samu a cikin bayanan haɗin kai na COVID-19 a cikin EU/EEA na kwanaki 14 da Burtaniya ya biyo bayan lardin Hubei (Cin) (Hoto 1).
A duk fadin EU/EEA da kuma Burtaniya, adadin mutanen da suka kamu da cutar COVID-19 ya fara tashi ne daga ranar 21 ga Fabrairu ya kai ranar 28 ga Fabrairu, 2020 (Matsakaicin).
Babban dalilin wannan tashin hankali shine yawan adadin wadanda aka samu a Italiya, yayin da sauran kasashen EU/EEA da Burtaniya suka nuna irin wannan ci gaban a cikin adadin COVID-19 (Abubuwa).
Hoto na 2 ya nuna jimillar adadin mutanen da suka kamu da cutar COVID-19, a cikin EU/EEA da UK da kuma Italiya a ranar 31 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020.
Ya ce, a ranar 15 ga watan Maris da karfe 8:00 na yamma, kasashe 15 na EU/EEA da wasu na Burtaniya sun sanar da adadin wadanda za a iya kamuwa da su da cutar a Italiya a cikin kwanaki uku kafin ko bayan karshen.
Wannan ya nuna cewa adadin mutanen da suka kamu da cutar COVID-19 ba su da yawa kamar yadda EU/EEA da Burtaniya suka yi.
Matsayin da muke tsammani na yaduwar COVID-19 yana nuna cewa cutar tana da daidaito da kuma yiwuwar a magance ta a duk ƙasashe.
Wannan ya faru ne saboda bambancin jihohi, canje-canje a cikin tsarin kula da lafiyar ƙasa, da kuma bambancin yanayin a cikin jihohi da kuma wasu matakai don zaɓin marasa lafiya waɗanda ke buƙatar sake gwadawa don COVID-19, da kuma sake gwadawa.
A farkon watan Maris na 2020, likitoci a yankunan da ke fama da cutar ta Italiya sun gano cewa kashi 10% na masu cutar COVID-19 sun buƙaci kulawa ta musamman kuma kafofin watsa labarai sun ce asibitoci da kungiyoyin kula da marasa lafiya a yankunan sun ci gaba da cimma hakan.
Bayanai game da asibitoci da/ko rukunin kula da marasa lafiya na COVID-19 suna cikin EU/EEA na kashi 6% da 1%, bi da bi (bayanai za a nuna).
Bayan haka, ana tattara su a cikin wani shafi don aika bayanan kulawa wanda ke nuna adadin marasa lafiya da mutuwar.
Wani bincike na 2010-2011 ya nuna bambancin da ke tattare da samun gadaje da umarnin kulawa a cikin marasa lafiya masu tsanani da marasa lafiya a Turai, daga gado 29.2 a Jamus zuwa 4.2 a cikin mutane 100,000 a Portugal.
A cewarsa, kasashe masu arziki za su iya zama masu arziki ko kuma marasa arziki kamar Italiya (12.5 na gadajen asibiti da kuma asibiti daya ga mutane 100,000 a 2010-11).
Shirya shirye-shiryen da suka shafi tsarin karbar bakuncin, tare da yiwuwar kowane EU/EEA da UK sun karɓi marasa lafiya na COVID-19 waɗanda ke buƙatar asibiti da kuma buƙatun gado waɗanda ke buƙatar samun umarnin kulawa na mutum aƙalla 90% a cikin jerin na shida na gwajin ECDC na gwajin cutar COVID-19.
Saboda yawan masu cutar da ke yaduwa a wasu sassan EU/EEA da sauran Burtaniya, da kuma asibitoci da kungiyoyin kula da marasa lafiya da ke aiki a wuraren kula da marasa lafiya, ana iya samun bayanai kan marasa lafiya da gadaje masu umarni a duk biranen da ke da ciwon daji na 2 (NUTS-2).
Abubuwan da suka faru a Italiya da kuma halin da ake ciki a wasu ƙasashe sun nuna cewa annobar COVID-19 ta ci gaba da yaduwa a cikin EU/EEA da Burtaniya.
Jihohi, asibitoci da kungiyoyin kula da marasa lafiya dole ne su tsara kansu kan yadda za su taimaka wa al'umma saboda cutar SARS-CoV-2 da karuwar adadin masu cutar COVID-19 da ke buƙatar kulawa ta musamman, kamar yadda ake samu a yankunan da ke fama da cutar a Italiya.
Kamar yadda aka lissafa a cikin binciken ECDC na cutar, akwai cikakkiyar hanyar da ba ta dace ba don hana yaduwar SARS-COV-2, da kuma hanyar da ta wuce daga magani zuwa raguwa, kamar yadda yawan adadin masu cutar ba zai ba da isasshen lokaci ga masu kula da lafiyar su fahimci, amsa da kuma daidaita tsarin amsawar su ba tare da lokaci ba.
