A ranar 26 ga watan Fabrairu, an samu adadin wadanda suka kamu da cutar a tsakanin matasa masu shekaru 19 zuwa sama, wanda ya kai kashi 2.4% na wadanda suka kamu da cutar a duniya. Shugaban hukumar kula da ilimin ilimin dan adam ta Burtaniya, Patrick Vallance, ya yi hasashen cewa kashi 60% na jama'ar Ingila dole ne su kamu da cutar kafin a sami ingantacciyar kariya a cikin al'umma.
Masu cutar sune adadin mutanen da suka gwada tabbatacce na COVID-19, kuma waɗanda ba a rarraba su ba kamar yadda aka lissafa a cikin bayanan gwamnati.
