bAngiotensin-converting enzyme 2 (ACE2) wani sinadarin da ke da muhimmanci a waje da jikin (kwayoyin) kwayoyin halitta a cikin huhu, jini, zuciya, jijiya, da kuma jijiyoyin jini.
ACE2 yana hana aikin aikin angiotensin-converting enzyme (ACE) ta hanyar rage haɓakar angiotensin-II da haɓaka Ang ((1-7)), wanda ya sa ya zama magani mai yuwuwa don magance cututtukan zuciya. ACE2 kuma yana aiki a matsayin ƙofa a cikin wasu ƙwayoyin cuta na coronavirus.
Kwayar cutar mutum tana da alaƙa da hACE2.
Angiotensin-converting protein 2 shine zinc-containing metalloenzyme kuma yana kan endothelial da sauran kwayoyin halitta.
Kwayar ACE2 tana da N-terminal peptidase M2 domain da kuma C-terminal collectrin renal amino acid transporter domain.
ACE2 shine mai shigar da kwayar halitta mai nau'in nau'in I, wanda ke dauke da sinadarin aiki kuma yana da tasiri a kan kwayoyin halitta a cikin huhu da sauran kwayoyin.
An haɗa yankin ACE2 na waje da kwayar halitta zuwa yankin transmembrane ta wani sinadarin da ake kira sheddase, kuma an sanya wannan furotin a cikin jini kuma daga ƙarshe ya fita daga cikin kwayar halitta.
ACE2 yana cikin yawancin kwayoyin halitta: ACE2 yana cikin kwayoyin halitta na kwayoyin halitta na alveolar type II, ƙananan ƙwayoyin cuta, ƙwayoyin arterial da venous endothelial da kuma ƙwayoyin arterial muscle a yawancin kwayoyin halitta.
An kuma gano tsarin ACE2 mRNA a cikin cerebral cortex, striatum, hypothalamus, da kuma kwakwalwar kwakwalwa.
Babban aikin ACE2 shine a matsayin mai daidaitawa a ACE.
ACE yana haifar da halayen angiotensin I ta hanyar halayen angiotensin II.
ACE2 kuma yana canza carboxyl-terminal amino acid phenylalanine daga angiotensin II (Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-Phe) ta hanyar mai narkar da jini na angiotensin (1-7), (H-Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-OH).
ACE2 na iya kuma sanya wasu peptides kamar [des-Arg9]-bradykinin, apelin, neurotensin, dynorphin A, da ghrelin.
ACE2 kuma yana hana kwayar cutar SLC6A19 kuma yana da tasiri a cutar Hartnup.
A matsayin furotin na transmembrane, ACE2 yana aiki a matsayin ƙofa ɗaya a cikin wasu ƙwayoyin cuta na coronaviruses, kamar HCoV-NL63; SARS-CoV (kwayar cutar da ke haifar da SARS); da SARS-CoV-2 (kwayar cutar da ke haifar da COVID-19).
A wani bangare kuma, haɗuwa da kwayar cutar S1 ta SARS-CoV da SARS-CoV2 a cikin enzymatic domain na ACE2 na ƙwayoyin cuta ya haifar da endocytosis da kuma sauyawar ƙwayoyin cuta biyu zuwa ƙwayoyin cuta na endosomes da ke cikin ƙwayoyin.
Wannan binciken ya hana samar da furotin S ta hanyar mai karɓar kwayar cutar TMPRSS2, wanda aka fara bincike a matsayin magani.Wannan ya haifar da tunanin cewa rage matakan ACE2 a cikin kwayoyin zai iya zama da amfani wajen magance cutar.
Koyaya, ƙungiyoyi da yawa na ƙwararru da hukumomin tsarawa sun ba da shawarar ci gaba da daidaitaccen maganin ACE inhibitor da ARB.
Binciken da aka yi na nazarin binciken da aka gudanar a ranar 11 ga Yuli, 2012, ya gano cewa "yin amfani da magungunan ACE yana da alaƙa da raguwar 34% na cutar huhu idan aka kwatanta da rigakafi".
Bugu da ƙari, "haɗarin cututtukan huhu ya ragu a cikin marasa lafiya da ke shan maganin ACE masu hanawa waɗanda ke da haɗarin kamuwa da cutar huhu, musamman a cikin waɗanda ke da cututtukan jini da cututtukan zuciya.
An kuma danganta rage shan maganin ACE da rage mutuwar masu fama da cutar huhu, ko da yake an rage yawan cutar huhu".
Recombinant human ACE2 (rhACE2) wani magani ne na zamani don magance cututtukan huhu, kuma yana taimakawa wajen rage yawan jini a cikin huhu da kuma isar da iska a cikin yara masu ciki waɗanda suka kamu da cutar ta lipopolysaccharide.
Rabin rayuwar rhACE2 a cikin mutum yana da kimanin minti 10 kuma farkon aikin shine minti 30 tare da haɓaka cikin haɗari (lokaci) a cikin awanni 24.
Yawancin bincike sun nuna cewa rhACE2 na iya zama magani mai mahimmanci ga mutanen da basu iya jurewa ga magungunan hana tsarin renin-angiotensin ba (RAS inhibitors) ko kuma a cikin cututtukan da angiotensin II ke da tasiri. An gwada rhACE2 da aka yi amfani da shi a cikin gwaji na asibiti don magance cututtukan huhu.
b'COVID-19 apps sune aikace-aikacen da aka kirkira don taimakawa gano mutane a cikin martani ga cutar coronavirus ta 2019-20, kamar yadda aka bayyana a cikin tsarin gano mutane ("abokan hulɗa") waɗanda zasu iya kasancewa tare da wanda ya kamu da cutar.
An gabatar da aikace-aikace da yawa ko kuma an ba da shawarar su, tare da taimakon gwamnati da kuma na mutum a wasu yankuna da larduna.
An gabatar da takamaiman bayani game da yadda ake bayyana aikace-aikacen haɗin kai.
